metadata.name: ZIPSharks Fishing License #1
metadata.description: ZIPSharks Fishing License is the ZIPSharks Communities exclusive pass to upcoming ZIPSharks future NFTs and products. The limited edition pass is reserved for the community of ZIPSharks initiative.  This pass is solely designed to award the owner by providing the best art, entertainment, and services provided by ZIPSharks. This includes but is not exclusive to giveaways, IRL events, product launches, and community intellectual property. Sharks swim forward, never stop, only look up, never down...
